data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
- If you are unfamilliar with the game minesweeper you can learn how to play at: https://www.wikihow.com/Play-Minesweeper
- The aim of the game is to gain more "score", each player can clear one space on the board per turn, which will grant 1 point.
- Every turn, there is a military question for each player, if answered correctly the player gains 1 score point.
- If a bomb is hit by either player then that player instantly loses the game.
- This game uses a login database and scoreboard of how many wins and losses for each player.
